#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.reciprocal.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.reciprocal"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.reciprocal.reciprocal:1 of
msgid "Return the reciprocal of the argument, element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素返回参数的倒数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.reciprocal.reciprocal:3 of
msgid "Calculates ``1/x``."
msgstr "计算 ``1/x``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.reciprocal.reciprocal of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.reciprocal.reciprocal:5 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.reciprocal.reciprocal:7 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入形状。如果未提供或"
"为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.reciprocal.reciprocal:12 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.reciprocal.reciprocal of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.reciprocal.reciprocal:17 of
msgid "**y** -- Return tensor."
msgstr "**y** -- 返回张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.reciprocal.reciprocal of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.reciprocal.reciprocal:21 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.reciprocal.reciprocal:23 of
msgid "This function is not designed to work with integers."
msgstr "此函数不适用于整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.reciprocal.reciprocal:25 of
msgid ""
"For integer arguments with absolute value larger than 1 the result is "
"always zero because of the way Python handles integer division.  For "
"integer zero the result is an overflow."
msgstr ""
"对于绝对值大于 1 的整数参数，由于 Python 处理整数除法的方式，结果总是零。"
"对于整数零，结果是溢出。"

